title: Çigköftem - Hutteldorferstr
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Fast food, Take-out, Middle Eastern, Turkish, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Fast food chain specializing in a Turkish vegetable pate made of grains, walnuts, tomato puree, sunflower oil, parsley and green onions that shape into little balls or fingers and put in wraps or with mixed plates.
